{"tid":2189832,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"嗚呀！！！好想去捷克布拉格睇下元祖連儂牆呀！！！","createTime":"2020-09-05T07:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T17:00:40.000Z","uid":81879,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1d875366c4ef40f9821025c402a1f831526ccb88","tid":2189832,"uid":81879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:17:41.000Z","msg":"連儂牆（Lennonova zed）喺捷克共和國布拉格修道院大廣場（Velkopřevorsk&eacute; n&aacute;měst&iacute;）。1988年開始，捷克人開始喺連儂牆寫低對共產主義同埋對政府嘅不滿，後尾喺查理大橋附近導致一場學生同差人之間嘅衝突，共有幾百人被捲入。家下牆上面嘅塗鴉多數同和平理念有關，亦成為咗遊客參觀嘅熱門景點。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/連儂牆\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E7%89%86&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs4xjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=3c52b8da\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/連儂牆</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nXnfQUr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnXnfQUr.jpg&h=b81516a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KcjaEOg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKcjaEOg.jpg&h=18afaa55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢排捷克幫台灣幫到出晒面，真係想好好懲罰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7560834dfbab954ab87bff195359c50defbdf2","tid":2189832,"uid":81879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0211546a5f31698e007bc151a238a00cc6548c","tid":2189832,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6571c71e096ead2450473949d99c05e732ec7a2e","tid":2189832,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite